&lt;h3&gt;About Us&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join Hovercraft to create high-profile, culturally influential work for leading brands. Projects include visual systems, campaigns, story-driven environments, immersive digital installations, and browser-based experiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;The Role&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for designers who think strategically and creatively across a variety of project types. Portfolios should demonstrate conceptual thinking, strategic insight, and exceptional craft. Multidisciplinary skills such as illustration, animation, or spatial design are a plus.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Take ideas from initial concept through execution alongside creatives, technologists, producers and leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop original design directions and refine work within established brand guidelines and visual centers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Combine conceptual thinking with craft and attention to detail&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adapt to different brand styles and visual directions, spotting opportunities for unexpected interactive, environmental, or animation outputs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Find outside inspiration, and bring new thinking and ideas into the studio.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What We’re Looking For&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2+ years of experience in a similar role&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in Figma or Adobe Creative Cloud&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A passion and hunger for learning and up-leveling your craft&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Portfolio showing solid fundamentals, attention to detail, inventive design thinking and high-level execution in brand experience work (spec work is welcome)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A collaborative team player that is motivated, pro-active and positive.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Multi-disciplinary interests in other media (illustration, animation, 3D, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
