&lt;p&gt;Hovercraft is a remote-first company, working primarily on Pacific and Mountain time. Anyone/anywhere in the United States is encouraged to apply. You must be eligible to work in the US.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At this time, we are unable to support employment arrangements that require E-Verify participation, including STEM OPT extensions. Additionally, we are not currently offering employment visa sponsorship for this role.&amp;nbsp;Candidates must be authorized to work in the United States on a full-time basis without current or future employer sponsorship requirements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We appreciate your interest in our team and encourage candidates whose work authorization aligns with these requirements to apply.&lt;/p&gt;
